OL,3,CFamily announces public memorial for
OL,4,CAnn Widdecombe later this year
OL,6,FA public memorial for Ann Widdecombe
OL,7,Fwill be held later this year, her
OL,8,Ffamily have said.
OL,10,FThe 78-year-old Reform UK spokeswoman
OL,11,Fand former Tory minister was found
OL,12,Fdead at her home in Haytor on
OL,13,FDartmoor, Devon, on July 9 with
OL,14,Fserious head injuries.
OL,16,FJoshua Kerry, 28, from Rotherham,
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire, appeared in court on
OL,18,FTuesday charged with her murder.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
