OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784783956
OL,3,CFamily announces public memorial for
OL,4,CAnn Widdecombe later this year
OL,6,FIn a statement, Miss Widdecombe's
OL,7,Ffamily said: "We understand that there
OL,8,Fis significant public interest in the
OL,9,Ffuneral of Ann Widdecombe.
OL,11,F"A private service for family and
OL,12,Fclose friends will be held in the
OL,13,Fcoming weeks, and invitations for this
OL,14,Fceremony have been distributed.
OL,16,F"A more public memorial will follow
OL,17,Flater in the year, the details of
OL,18,Fwhich will be released in due course.
OL,26,@oD@NOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
