OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784783956
OL,3,CFamily announces public memorial for
OL,4,CAnn Widdecombe later this year
OL,6,F"While we are very grateful for the
OL,7,Fwide expression of condolences, the
OL,8,Ffamily would ask that this initial
OL,9,Fservice is limited to those closest to
OL,10,FAnn."
OL,12,FProsecutors say that on July 8, Miss
OL,13,FWiddecombe had been eating lunch when
OL,14,FKerry allegedly pulled up outside the
OL,15,Ffront of her bungalow in a red
OL,16,FVauxhall Corsa and entered through the
OL,17,Ffront door.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
