PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784783956
OL,3,CFamily announces public memorial for
OL,4,CAnn Widdecombe later this year
OL,6,FKerry then allegedly used a hammer to
OL,7,Fhit Miss Widdecombe on the top of her
OL,8,Fhead 21 times, the Old Bailey heard on
OL,9,FTuesday.
OL,11,FA provisional cause of death was given
OL,12,Fas a blunt force injury to the head,
OL,13,Fthe court heard.
OL,15,FDetectives are still investigating any
OL,16,Fpossible political or terrorist
OL,17,Fmotivation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
